In the MATTER OF TY HYDERALLY, An Attorney At Law (Attorney No. 023231993) D-24 September Term 2018
081931 Supreme Court of New Jersey. October 22, 2018

ORDER

This matter having been duly presented, it is ORDERED that Ty Hyderally of Montclair, who was admitted to the bar of this State in 1994, and who was suspended from the practice of law for a period of three months effective July 20, 2018, by Order of this Court filed June 22, 2018, be restored to the practice of law, effective immediately.
